trans-unit.source: An interface that is implemented by classes which are responsible for generating [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] content on behalf of a host.
trans-unit.target: Uma interface implementada pelo classes que são responsáveis por gerar [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] conteúdo em nome de um anfitrião.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> is the base class for containing and displaying one or more data items.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>é a classe base para que contém e apresentar um ou mais itens de dados.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator> maintains an association between <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> and the list of items that are displayed by <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator>mantém uma associação entre <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>e a lista de itens que são apresentados por <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl></xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator> is also responsible for generating the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] for those items on behalf of <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator>Também é responsável pela geração o [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] para esses itens em nome <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl></xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.VirtualizingPanel>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.VirtualizingStackPanel> also use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator> for the same reason.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.VirtualizingPanel>, e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.VirtualizingStackPanel>também utilizar <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator>pela mesma razão.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.VirtualizingStackPanel> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.VirtualizingPanel></xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator> implements IItemContainerGenerator and is the interface through which each of the mentioned layout elements communicate with <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator>implementa IItemContainerGenerator e é a interface através do qual cada dos elementos de esquema mencionadas comunicar com <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator></xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator>

trans-unit.source: Returns the container element used to display the next item.
trans-unit.target: Devolve o elemento de contentor utilizado para mostrar o item seguinte.

trans-unit.source: GenerateNext must be called within the scope of the <xref:System.IDisposable> reference that is returned by a previous call to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator.StartAt%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Tem de chamar generatenext quando no âmbito do <xref:System.IDisposable>referência que é devolvida por uma chamada anterior para o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator.StartAt%2A>método.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator.StartAt%2A> </xref:System.IDisposable>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.DependencyObject"></xref> that is the container element which is used to display the next item.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Windows.DependencyObject"> </xref> que é o elemento de contentor que é utilizado para apresentar o item seguinte.

trans-unit.source: Returns the container element used to display the next item, and whether the container element has been newly generated (realized).
trans-unit.target: Devolve o elemento de contentor utilizado para mostrar o item seguinte, e se o elemento do contentor foi recentemente gerado (realizados).

trans-unit.source: When the next item to be displayed has not already been generated (realized), GenerateNext returns a new <xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject>, otherwise, the existing <xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject> is returned.
trans-unit.target: Quando o item seguinte para ser apresentada não já foi gerado (realizados), generatenext quando devolve um novo <xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject>, caso contrário, o existente <xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject>é devolvido.</xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject> </xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject>

trans-unit.source: Is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the returned <xref href="System.Windows.DependencyObject"></xref> is newly generated (realized); otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: É <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> se o devolvido <xref href="System.Windows.DependencyObject"> </xref> recentemente é gerado (realizados); caso contrário, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.DependencyObject"></xref> that is the container element which is used to display the next item.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Windows.DependencyObject"> </xref> que é o elemento de contentor que é utilizado para apresentar o item seguinte.

trans-unit.source: Returns the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"></xref> object that maps to the item at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Devolve o <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"> </xref> objeto que está mapeado para o item no índice especificado.

trans-unit.source: The index of desired item.
trans-unit.target: O índice do item pretendido.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"></xref> object that maps to the item at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"> </xref> objeto que está mapeado para o item no índice especificado.

trans-unit.source: Returns the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator"></xref> appropriate for use by the specified panel.
trans-unit.target: Devolve o <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator"> </xref> adequado para utilização pelo painel especificado.

trans-unit.source: The panel for which to return an appropriate <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: O painel para o qual devolver apropriadas <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator"></xref> appropriate for use by the specified panel.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator"> </xref> adequado para utilização pelo painel especificado.

trans-unit.source: Returns the index that maps to the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Devolve o índice que mapeia para especificado <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The index of desired item.
trans-unit.target: O índice do item pretendido.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"></xref> for the desired index.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"> </xref> para o índice pretendido.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Int32> that is the index which maps to the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Int32>que é o índice que mapeia para especificado <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"> </xref>.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: Prepares the specified element as the container for the corresponding item.
trans-unit.target: Prepara o elemento especificado como o contentor para o item correspondente.

trans-unit.source: Preparing the specified element includes applying the container style, forwarding information from the host control, such as the <xref:System.Windows.DataTemplate> value of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemTemplate%2A> property, and other small adjustments.
trans-unit.target: Preparar o elemento especificado inclui aplicar o estilo de contentor, reencaminhamento informações do controlo de anfitrião, tais como o <xref:System.Windows.DataTemplate>valor o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemTemplate%2A>propriedade e outros ajustes pequenos.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemTemplate%2A> </xref:System.Windows.DataTemplate>

trans-unit.source: PrepareItemContainer must be called after the element has been added to the visual tree, so that resource references and inherited properties work correctly.
trans-unit.target: PrepareItemContainer tem de ser chamado depois do elemento foi adicionado à árvore visual, para que faz referência a recursos e herdada propriedades trabalho corretamente.

trans-unit.source: The container to prepare.
trans-unit.target: O contentor para preparar.

trans-unit.source: Normally, `container` is the result of the previous call to <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator.GenerateNext*>.
trans-unit.target: Normalmente, `container` é o resultado da chamada anterior para <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator.GenerateNext*>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator.GenerateNext*>

trans-unit.source: Removes one or more generated (realized) items.
trans-unit.target: Remove uma ou mais gerado itens (as).

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Int32> index of the element to remove.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Int32>do elemento para remover o índice.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: `position` must refer to a previously generated (realized) item, which means its offset must be zero.
trans-unit.target: `position`tem de referenciar um item (as) gerado anteriormente, o que significa que o desvio tem de ser zero.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Int32> number of elements to remove, starting at `position`.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Int32>número de elementos para remover, começando `position`.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: Removes all generated (realized) items.
trans-unit.target: Remove todos os gerado itens (as).

trans-unit.source: Prepares the generator to generate items, starting at the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"></xref>, and in the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorDirection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Prepara o gerador de gerar itens, começando especificado <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"> </xref>e em especificado <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorDirection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: StartAt must be called before <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator.GenerateNext%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: StartAt tem de ser chamado antes de <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator.GenerateNext%2A>é chamado.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator.GenerateNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: StartAt sets <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.Status%2A> to <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorStatus>; when the <xref:System.IDisposable> is disposed, the status changes to <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorStatus> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorStatus>, as appropriate.
trans-unit.target: Conjuntos de StartAt <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.Status%2A>para <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorStatus>; quando a <xref:System.IDisposable>é eliminado, o estado é alterado para <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorStatus>ou <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorStatus>, conforme adequado.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorStatus> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorStatus> </xref:System.IDisposable> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorStatus> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.Status%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"></xref>, that specifies the position of the item to start generating items at.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"> </xref>, que especifica a posição do item para iniciar a geração de itens em.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorDirection"></xref> that specifies the direction which to generate items.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorDirection"> </xref> que especifica a direcção para a geração de itens.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.IDisposable> object that tracks the lifetime of the generation process.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.IDisposable>objeto que controla a duração do processo de geração.</xref:System.IDisposable>

trans-unit.source: Prepares the generator to generate items, starting at the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"></xref>, and in the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorDirection"></xref>, and controlling whether or not to start at a generated (realized) item.
trans-unit.target: Prepara o gerador de gerar itens, começando especificado <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"> </xref>e em especificado <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorDirection"> </xref>e controlar se deve ou não iniciar um item (as) gerado.

trans-unit.source: See <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator.StartAt%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Consulte <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator.StartAt%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator.StartAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"></xref>, that specifies the position of the item to start generating items at.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.GeneratorPosition"> </xref>, que especifica a posição do item para iniciar a geração de itens em.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the position of the item to start generating items at.
trans-unit.target: Especifica a posição do item para iniciar a geração de itens em.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Boolean> that specifies whether to start at a generated (realized) item.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Boolean>que especifica se pretende iniciar o um item (as) gerado.</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.IDisposable> object that tracks the lifetime of the generation process.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.IDisposable>objeto que controla a duração do processo de geração.</xref:System.IDisposable>
